<HEADLINE> Sosa Hits Home Run No. 63 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	ST. LOUIS (AP) -- Sammy Sosa homered for the first time in 18  
at-bats, hitting No. 63 shortly after Mark McGwire hit his 65th in 
the Cubs-Cardinals game Sunday. 
