<HEADLINE> Ventura To Schwarzenegger: Don't Run </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	ST. PAUL, Minn. (AP) -- Gov. Jesse Ventura has urged his friend,  
actor Arnold Schwarzenegger, not to run for governor of California. 
</P>
<P>
	``My advice to Arnold, as a friend, is `Continue with your movie  
career, Arnold, don't get involved in it. It won't be worth it to 
you,''' Ventura said Sunday on ``Meet the Press.'' 
</P>
